Package org.fhnw.aigs.client.GUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseBoard
    The abstract BaseBoard class offers a convenient base class for classic board games like chess.
    BaseGameWindow
    This class provides represents the "frame" around a game.
    BaseHeader
    Provides a simple header for the GameWindow.
    GameEndWindow
    A simple screen which can be shown, when the winning conditions have been met.
    LoadingWindow
    This screen can be used to inform the user about the fact that there is either no player to join the game with or that the connection has not been established yet.
    SettingsWindow
    This class is responsible for the client settings.
    SettingsWindow.CheckAndCreateAction
    Validates the content and saves through Setting class IdentificationMessage.
    SettingsWindow.CloseWindowAdapter
    Handles close action.
